description:
Hermitcraft Season 10 is here! Join us as we settle down in a new world, build cool stuff, and have a good time with the other Hermits.

In this episode we go caving, explore the new map with Gem, find our base location, get our tools enchanted, clear cut a forest and then start building our future base.

Hermitcraft Website: http://www.hermitcraft.com
